a helper to the Publishing Committee,

00:09:28.817 --> 00:09:32.362 line:90% position:50% align:center
will now present the next talk
of this symposium,

00:09:32.362 --> 00:09:36.617 line:90% position:50% align:center
“‘Put Away’ Peace Wreckers—Dishonesty.”

